My Work

Health Chat

Health Chat is a mobile app that I designed as part of Career Foundry’s UX Design Course. It allows people to connect with experts in any health or wellness related field to get advice.

Tools used: Adobe XD, Google Draw, Surveys, Personal interviews, preference tests

Fit Now

Fit Now is a responsive web app designed for Career Foundry’s UI for UX Design course. It helps people find exercises and workouts that suit their skill level and interests.

Tools used: Adobe Photoshop, Adobe Illustrator, Adobe Indesign, Adobe XD, InVision
